Kwon Jin Ah's new song ‘This winter,’ which is her first winter song, will be released after a long time since her digital single "Fly away" released last year. ‘This winter,’ sung by Kwon Jin Ah, who has been a storyteller specializing in ‘separation’ with her outstanding singing and emotions now will deliver the different look about beginning of love. While she was busy preparing her new album, she made a surprise comeback with the song, ‘This winter,’ which she wrote for the winter.
